title: Nultiplicities can be inspected in the repl.
pid: 14e92d09-a5f8-4953-9a88-5ea18d751a63
body: |2-
  append : Vect n a -> Vect m a -> Vect (n + m) a
  append xs ys = ?append_rhs
  …we can look at the hole append_rhs:

  Main> :t append_rhs
   0 m : Nat
   0 a : Type
   0 n : Nat
     ys : Vect m a
     xs : Vect n a
  -------------------------------------
  append_rhs : Vect (plus n m) a
